{"tid":920376,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明愛3眼科醫生涉不當轉介病人及偷藥 遭廉署起訴","createTime":"2018-11-28T18:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T19:40:19.000Z","uid":80516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a02803eeb97d02cd154c7932f8c9d9bad05d37e","tid":920376,"uid":80516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=BEUgg9UfG23NtCXPAgLaf1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=7d4f3f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】3名明愛醫院前眼科醫生，分別涉嫌串謀公職人員行為失當，轉介醫管局病人至其中二人所開設的私家眼科診所，以及盜竊醫管局藥物，被廉署落案起訴他們串謀犯公職人員行為失當及盜竊等罪。3名被告獲准保釋，將於周五(30日)在西九龍裁判法院應訊，以待案件轉介區域法院答辯。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告分別為邱承建(39歲)、朱東麒(45歲)及朱東恒(42歲)。3人同被控一項串謀犯公職人員行為失當罪名，邱及朱東麒另被控一項相類罪名，而朱東麒及朱東恒亦被控一項相類罪名。此外，邱另被控一項盜竊罪名。<br />\n<br />\n案發時，邱承建於為明愛醫院眼科部全職醫生，朱東麒自2011年8月起出任明愛眼科部兼職醫生，而其弟朱東恒則由2016年5月起由全職轉任兼職明愛眼科部醫生；朱氏兄弟亦在尖沙咀經營一所私家眼科診所。3人於明愛眼科部工作期間，其中一項職責是提供眼科臨床及專科服務。在臨床服務方面，他們會治療病人，記錄其診斷及管理其醫療紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩項控罪指邱承建、朱東麒及/或朱東恒涉嫌於2012年1月4日至2016年6月21日期間，一同串謀使邱轉介那些由他於明愛醫院診治的病人，到該尖沙咀診所並改向朱東麒及/或朱東恒尋求診治，並向朱東麒及/或朱東恒披露該些病人的資料及紀錄，及在該尖沙咀診所從事外間工作，違反醫管局相關指引及政策。<br />\n<br />\n另一項控罪指朱氏兄弟涉嫌於2012年1月4日至於2016年6月8日期間，一同串謀使朱東恒轉介那些由他於明愛醫院診治的病人，到其尖沙咀診所並改向朱東麒求診，及向朱東麒披露該些病人的資料及紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n餘下一項控罪指邱承建涉嫌於2016年5月26日從醫管局偷竊29瓶滴眼劑及9支眼藥膏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r7vDAvj7qCLgIQna1sBGHw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/33501d9c3c41692f5e484b22284cd874\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fr7vDAvj7qCLgIQna1sBGHw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F33501d9c3c41692f5e484b22284cd874&h=f6ac4216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V_FyfBBcIVPMvIPderLJvg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/29bb67e2668be8108d64eee183d1fb4a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FV_FyfBBcIVPMvIPderLJvg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F29bb67e2668be8108d64eee183d1fb4a&h=ccee55df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uSOP2guW9HG0H9947hAyQA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/onccinstantnews.com/89e9601f10ecbbdbdd7a836d6ee15b96\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuSOP2guW9HG0H9947hAyQA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F89e9601f10ecbbdbdd7a836d6ee15b96&h=8b87dfd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"131bd7363ed2b2864a82c8bb8d8dc85daa74cfee","tid":920376,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2725a3b6aa57c5bebf9d568327f2a689829b6e2","tid":920376,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:38:03.000Z","msg":"三眼仔都做到醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a065c6e0088592bec28b106fc6647dca2b8a96dd","tid":920376,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:40:19.000Z","msg":"冇生意到咁？"}]}